adDetails: The rental unit is for a Weekend Warrior 28 feet tow hauler. Comes with all the amenities and a 1/2 ton pickup or an SUV can pull this bad boy. Must have a hitch to tow. Please provide your number if you have any questions. $130 per day and 4 day minimum. We also offer a F350 dually rental for additional $125 if you have no truck to pull.
